###################  user
### Get users in realms
GET {{host}}/admin/realms/sso/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create user in realms
POST {{host}}/admin/realms/{{realm}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "username":"oom2",
    "email":"oom2@xxx.com",
    "enabled":true,
    "credentials":[
        {
            "temporary":false,
            "type":"password",
            "value":"oom2"
        }
    ]
}

### Get a user by name
GET {{host}}/admin/realms/{{realm}}/users/?username=mam
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete user
DELETE {{host}}/admin/realms/sso/users/{{{user_uuid}}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



####### Client
### Find id of express-client
GET {{host}}/admin/realms/{{realm}}/clients/?clientId=express-client
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



###
GET {{host}}/admin/realms/{{realm}}/groups/{group-id}/role-mappings/clients/{client-id}/available
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


######## Roles 
### Get role list in express-client
GET {{host}}/admin/realms/{{realm}}/clients/{{client_uuid}}/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Role avaliable to user
GET {{host}}/admin/realms/{{realm}}/users/{{user_uuid}}/role-mappings/clients/{{client_uuid}}/available
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Role by name
GET {{host}}/admin/realms/{{realm}}/clients/{{client_uuid}}/roles/dev
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


